%AI_Design_Template_for_Spout_Pouch
%Package_Lab_Epackage_Design_Template
%Japanese_Market_Standard_Dimensions

Template_Name: スパウトパウチ (Spout Pouch)
Product_Category: spout_pouch
Standard_Sizes:
  - 120mm x 200mm (with 18mm spout)
  - 150mm x 250mm (with 22mm spout)
  - 180mm x 300mm (with 25mm spout)
  - 200mm x 320mm (with 28mm spout)

Design_Specifications:
  - Bleed: 3mm on all edges
  - Safety Zone: 5mm from edges
  - File Format: Adobe Illustrator CS6 or later
  - Color Mode: CMYK
  - Resolution: 300 DPI
  - Spout placement: Top center or top corner

Cutting_Guides:
  - Solid line: Final cut line
  - Circle: Spout opening
  - Dashed line: Cap attachment line

Design_Elements:
  [Front_Panel]
  - Product logo area: Top center (above spout)
  - Product name: Below logo
  - Product description: Center area
  - Weight/Volume: Bottom left
  - Barcode area: Bottom right
  - Serving size info: Above bottom

  [Back_Panel]
  - Ingredients list: Top area
  - Instructions: Center area
  - Manufacturer info: Bottom area
  - Expiry date: Bottom right
  - Storage conditions: Bottom left

  [Spout_Area]
  - Clear zone around spout: 15mm radius
  - "Twist to open" instruction
  - Arrow indicators for opening direction
  - Warning: "Do not microwave with cap"

Color_Guidelines:
  - Primary colors: Brand specific
  - Text color: High contrast (minimum 60%)
  - Background: Consider liquid visibility
  - Spout area: Clear for transparent options

Special_Features:
  - Liquid-friendly design
  - Easy pouring mechanism
  - Leak-proof construction
  - Re-sealable cap
  - Handle options for larger sizes
  - Transparent window for content visibility

Usage_Instructions_Area:
  - Step 1: Twist cap to open
  - Step 2: Pour gently
  - Step 3: Close cap tightly
  - Storage: Refrigerate after opening (if applicable)

Safety_Information:
  - Keep away from children under 3 years
  - Do not squeeze when hot
  - Check seal integrity before use

File_Naming_Convention:
  - Client_Project_ProductCode_Size.ai
  - Example: Epackage_Juice_Brand_SpoutPouch_150x250.ai

